\c 12
\s Ukubizwa kukaAbrama
\p
\v 1 IN\sc KOSI\sc* yasisithi kuAbrama: Suka wena elizweni lakini lezihlotsheni zakho lemzini kayihlo, uye elizweni engizakutshengisa lona\x + Seb. 7.3. Heb. 11.8.\x*.
\v 2 Ngizakwenza-ke ube yisizwe esikhulu, ngikubusise, ngenze ibizo lakho libe likhulu, njalo ube yisibusiso.
\v 3 Njalo ngizababusisa abakubusisayo, labakuqalekisayo ngibaqalekise\x + 27.29. Nani 24.9.\x*; lakuwe kuzabusiswa zonke insapho zomhlaba\x + 18.18; 22.18; 26.4; 28.14. Seb. 3.25. Gal. 3.8.\x*.
\v 4 UAbrama wasehamba njengoba iN\sc KOSI\sc* ikhulumile kuye, loLothi wahamba laye. Njalo uAbrama wayeleminyaka engamatshumi ayisikhombisa lanhlanu ekusukeni kwakhe eHarani.
\v 5 UAbrama wasethatha uSarayi umkakhe, loLothi indodana yomfowabo, lempahla yabo yonke ababeyiqoqile, lemiphefumulo ababeyizuzile\x + 14.14.\x* eHarani\x + 11.31.\x*; basebesuka ukuya elizweni leKhanani; bafika elizweni leKhanani.
\p
\v 6 UAbrama wasedabula ilizwe\x + Heb. 11.9.\x* waze wafika endaweni yeShekema, esihlahleni se-okhi*\x + 13.18.\x* seMore\x + Dute. 11.30. Hlu. 7.1.\x*. LamaKhanani ayekhona elizweni\x + 10.18,19; 13.7.\x* ngalesosikhathi.
\v 7 IN\sc KOSI\sc* yasibonakala kuAbrama, yathi: Kunzalo yakho ngizanika lelilizwe\x + 13.15; 17.8. Hlab. 105.9-12.\x*. Waseyakhela lapho iN\sc KOSI\sc* ilathi eyayibonakale kuye.
\v 8 Waseqhubeka esuka lapho waya entabeni empumalanga yeBhetheli, wamisa ithente lakhe, iBhetheli entshonalanga leAyi empumalanga. Waseyakhela lapho iN\sc KOSI\sc* ilathi, wabiza ibizo leN\sc KOSI\x + 13.4.\x*\sc*.
\v 9 UAbrama wasesuka wahamba eqhubeka esiya eningizimu.
\s UAbrama useGibithe
\p
\v 10 Kwaba khona-ke indlala elizweni\x + 26.1.\x*. UAbrama wasesehlela ngaseGibithe ukuthi ahlale khona njengowezizwe, ngoba indlala yayinzima elizweni\x + 43.1.\x*.
\v 11 Kwasekusithi esesondela ukungena eGibithe wathi kuSarayi umkakhe: Khangela-ke, ngiyazi ukuthi ungowesifazana omuhle obukekayo.
\v 12 Njalo kuzakuthi lapho amaGibithe ekubona, azakuthi: Lo ngumkakhe; abesengibulala\x + 20.1-18; 26.6-11.\x*, kodwa wena akugcine uphila.
\v 13 Ake uthi ungudadewethu, ukuze kube kuhle kimi ngenxa yakho, lomphefumulo wami uphile ngenxa yakho.
\v 14 Kwasekusithi lapho uAbrama esefikile eGibithe, amaGibithe ambona owesifazana, ukuthi muhle kakhulu.
\v 15 Iziphathamandla zikaFaro lazo zambona, zambabaza phambi kukaFaro. Owesifazana waselethwa endlini kaFaro.
\v 16 Wasemphatha kuhle uAbrama ngenxa yakhe; njalo waba lezimvu lezinkabi labobabhemi lezinceku lezincekukazi labobabhemikazi lamakamela.
\v 17 Kodwa iN\sc KOSI\sc* yamhlupha uFaro ngezinhlupheko ezinkulu\x + 20.18. 1 Lan. 16.21. Hlab. 105.14.\x*, lendlu yakhe, ngendaba kaSarayi umkaAbrama.
\v 18 UFaro wasembiza uAbrama, wathi: Kuyini lokhu okwenze kimi? Kungani ungangitshelanga ukuthi ungumkakho?
\v 19 Utsholoni ukuthi ungudadewenu, ngize ngimthathe ukuba ngumkami? Ngakho khangela-ke umkakho; \add m\add*thathe uhambe.
\v 20 UFaro waselaya amadoda ngaye; asemxotsha lomkakhe lakho konke ayelakho.
